{"tid":35510,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［秒回］分咗手一個月 好想挽回","createTime":"2016-12-12T06:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T08:55:45.000Z","uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"add63a69a1de79f778d06dcb8a80f035c8581085","tid":35510,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:39:26.000Z","msg":"我地一齊咗差唔多兩年<br />\n佢同我分咗手一個月 佢對我已經死心咗好多<br />\n而且話唔想再一齊 就算我講咩佢已經開始覺得我煩<br />\n我好想挽回 我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ecc408e136431eef18b43b785e3cd84b854e9b","tid":35510,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"咩事先，不過冇用嫁啦，女人都係雞"},{"pid":"15afffaf25410e69ca570ea9fb3832c9444d6cc1","tid":35510,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:40:20.000Z","msg":"有冇人有同樣經歷<br />\n有冇人係到可以傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6396157ac7417ff580885087badd42c12febfd","tid":35510,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:40:33.000Z","msg":"關我撚事？"},{"pid":"8043d978d4cc084470c8f13d69bcad131ec20417","tid":35510,"uid":38642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"裝備好自己 裝裝下就會唔記得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7883eec40d40d435b8f7db302c58d03cb15dd7","tid":35510,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩事先，不過冇用嫁啦，女人都係雞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前同會分過一次手 冇第三者 <br />\n我覺得同佢拍拖好似好唔被重視 覺得好攰<br />\n分咗手一個星期到就一齊返 但嗰一個星期佢講咗好多野挽留我 但我都好猶豫仲有啲絕<br />\n然後復合返佢就覺得已經死心咗好多 最後就分咗一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b1ef6fe831eef0b0f4b3e10a00829aeea49ea3","tid":35510,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關我撚事？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔關 淨係想問下意見"},{"pid":"d207c5c26492228a3a52282accc0e32036b1a980","tid":35510,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>裝備好自己 裝裝下就會唔記得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔想放低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea422f599bc23c864f827b353d1af5c91f3cc6c","tid":35510,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b4dd117e908cb9a6053b7b8d7de4faca7e767e8","tid":35510,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"女人絕情起上來你估都估唔到<br />\n你自己就回憶緊浪漫歷史<br />\n行街旅行一齊玩玩食食sweet野係個腦到loop<br />\n佢頂籠咪傷心一陣 過幾日訓返幾覺乜都唔記得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9774434a048a8bb75e9a278591b202d8421eebe3","tid":35510,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>溝過個la ching，變左心冇ga la</blockquote><br />\n佢唔係變心 冇第三者出現"},{"pid":"225f5ac29eda55d06235db253dd183d2a4c42ec6","tid":35510,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人絕情起上來你估都估唔到<br />\n你自己就回憶緊浪漫歷史<br />\n行街旅行一齊玩玩食食sweet野係個腦到loop<br />\n佢頂籠咪傷心一陣 過幾日訓返幾覺乜都唔記得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢仲有因為我地嘅事而喊<br />\n係咪都冇機會"},{"pid":"da191e11ab2b9fe063284b27d268879e7ae1d59f","tid":35510,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:46:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08be030577bdfbb71f4e684171c8684f2fa63fa4","tid":35510,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:46:36.000Z","msg":"如果可以我願意用任何代價同你一齊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af92bfcb541ef0aaff751573b4e1eb42456feec1","tid":35